        {
            "title": "孟加拉國判處前總理哈西娜21年監禁 此前她已被判死刑",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 孟加拉國一家法院因多起腐敗案件判處前總理<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:哈西娜;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/哈西娜\">哈西娜</a>21年監禁。哈西娜此前已因去年暴力鎮壓學生抗議而被判處死刑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈西娜去年逃往印度，法庭進行了缺席審判。反腐敗委員會首席協調員Khan Mohammad Moinul Hasan在接受彭博新聞社採訪時表示，哈西娜被判犯有腐敗罪，就對她的三項指控法院分別判處7年徒刑。他還補充說，這些刑期「將逐一執行，而不是同時執行」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：孟加拉國特別法庭判處流亡前領導人哈西娜死刑</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-22a3a1e0-f0d2-31c3-9b8c-a082f85873f2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"哈西娜攝影：克里斯托弗·派克/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6yNSpxqXdpXVpEkRH208cA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/49a23847f17fb30fbeadf112808949be\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">哈西娜攝影：克里斯托弗·派克/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hasan引述法院判決說，法院裁定哈西娜在擔任國家最高領導人期間，與高級官員勾結並違反規定，以獲取高價值地塊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">哈西娜在聲明中說：「我們堅決否認所有腐敗指控，針對我們的每一項指控都帶有我們對手的政治動機。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hasan說，法院還判處哈西娜的兒子薩吉布·瓦吉德和女兒賽瑪·瓦吉德5年監禁，罪名是他們參與了「非法分配國有土地」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bangladesh Hands Ex-Leader 21 Years in Jail After Death Penalty</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%A4%E8%99%95%E5%89%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E5%93%88%E8%A5%BF%E5%A8%9C21%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%A3%E7%A6%81-%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E5%A5%B9%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E6%AD%BB%E5%88%91-010445882.html",
